data.description: This Charming Historical Victorian Style Home Stands as one of the most Significant Examples of Restoration and Preservation in the Heart of Parsippany! Its Massive Scale, Singular Architectural Style and Unobstructed Location, is considered one of the Most Visually Striking Home in Parsippany!  Lower Level features Original Wide-Plank Flooring Throughout along with Multiple Office/Den Spaces along with a Newly Finished Full Bathroom, and Convenient Butler's Pantry.  Custom Moldings and Original Finishings attribute to this Lovely Preserved Masterpiece!  2nd Floor features Generously sized Bedrooms, Living Room, Eat In Kitchen with Cathedral Ceiling , Natural Gas Range, Newer Appliances and Built In Shelves. Gorgeously Landscaped Backyard featuring a Well and Barn/Stable for Storage Galore!  Basement is accessible by Bilco Doors and offers Ample Storage Space! With its Newer Roof, Newer Utilities, Low Taxes, and Prestigious Parsippany School District, this Gem is not to be MISSED!!
